Here is some code I use to find out how many stack space is used after a
run. I guess it won't work in protected mode. Be aware
it isn't byte-resolution ! I'd like to hear about enhancements.
}

unit Stack;
interface
  procedure InitStack;
  procedure TestStack;
implementation

